Weather-OWM

Weather::OWM - Perl client for the OpenWeatherMap (OWM) API

INSTALLATION

Normally you would expect to use a package manager like cpanm to install as:

    cpanm Weather::OWM

But to install this module manually, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

CPAN:
    https://metacpan.org/pod/Weather::OWM

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Weather::OWM

Source code and issues on GitHub:
    https://github.com/dkechag/Weather-OWM

